This Package defines Android independant api as interfaces to handle geo infos.

    IGeoInfoConverter<R extends IGeoPointInfo>

    IGeoInfoHandler
    Defines callback for processing IGeoPointInfo items.

Package de.k3b.geo.api Description

This Package defines Android independant api as interfaces to handle geo infos.

  • IGeoPointInfo implemented by GeoPointDto: a location or trackpoint that can be represented in a gpx file.
  • GpxFormatter: Formats ILocation-s, IGeoPointInfo, GeoPointDto-s or as geo-xml.
  • IGeoRepository implemented as GpxReader: reads GeoPointDto from file or stream.
